---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="kanban" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Agile PM</h2>
		<p>With over 3 years of experience leading cross-functional teams, I use Agile Scrum to deliver <strong>high-impact digital solutions</strong>. My work includes integrating Uber's Delivery Option on the EB Games website and designing the Digital Student ID experience at CQUniversity.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Software Developer</h2>
		<p>For over 7 years in software development, I have built <strong>scalable web applications and internal systems</strong>. Specialising in modern web technologies, backend architecture, and API-driven development, I create solutions that enhance the user experience.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="plant" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Innovator in XR & AI</h2>
		<p>Exploring <strong>XR, AI and spatial computing</strong>, I develop projects that push the boundaries of immersive experiences. My latest project, <strong>Smash Room</strong>, has surpassed 1,000 downloads on Meta Quest and Steam, blending real-world interactions with physics-based gameplay.</p>
	</div>

</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
